                            <comment id="14246543" author="stephanewen" created="Mon, 15 Dec 2014 10:50:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Any updates or other opinions on that? Otherwise, let&apos;s add to the Java / Scala Docs that we assume that the data is not modified...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
